---
// ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
// ║  REMOVABLE BANNER — delete when migration is complete            ║
// ║                                                                  ║
// ║  To remove this banner:                                          ║
// ║    1. Delete this file: src/components/MigrationBanner.astro     ║
// ║    2. Remove the import line in projects/index.astro:            ║
// ║         import MigrationBanner from                              ║
// ║           '../../components/MigrationBanner.astro';             ║
// ║    3. Remove the tag in projects/index.astro:                    ║
// ║         <MigrationBanner />                                      ║
// ║                                                                  ║
// ║  Target removal date: 13 July 2026                               ║
// ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
---

<div class="w-full bg-red-700 text-white" role="banner">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-4">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
      <svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126ZM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008Z" />
      </svg>
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-base leading-snug tracking-tight">Projects migration in progress</p>
        <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-red-100">I recently graduated with a 1st Class Honours BSc in Computer Science.</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-red-100">
          University coursework projects and personal projects are currently being migrated to this portfolio.
          Migration is estimated to be complete by <strong class="font-semibold text-white">13 July 2026</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
